Extended ER features 

Specialization
This cover the division of the poeple in several group and division of their entity  . 
This division of the same entitiy and theier attributes make the division  make the specialisation better .


The example to this specialisation is that in a class Person  : This peroson can be divided into the sub sets of the customer and employee . The attibute of the age maybe the employee id and the cusotmer maybe some passcode . 
This is the way the specialisation of the reosure are done in the Extended ER diagram . 

The child entity here in the abive example are the Customer and the employee class also the Person's attribute are being taken or can be inhertiend by the two class .
